{
  "stem": "3206.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He organized the whole city, practically-- the whole city-- boys, young boys, Christian boys.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they came, in while I was going out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They wanted to catch me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't bother anybody else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They wanted to catch me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you know, probably they would have killed me that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I have seen-- I was the last one out from this school, and I've seen what's going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the boys started to yell, run away, because they're going to kill you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I ran back to the school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And our school was situated-- like a cemetery was behind the school, a Jewish cemetery an old-- called Old Jewish Cemetery.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was a wall all around that cemetery, a big wall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And you know, you have monuments there and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I ran back to the school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I opened up a window, and I jumped out through the window to the cemetery at night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At night, and I was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That time, I was 10 years old, maybe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And through the cemetery, I ran to the end of the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I jumped over the fence-- that big fence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I came home through the back door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I came into the house, and I passed out, because as a young boy, you know, to go in a cemetery at night, this was-- this was not heard of in the small towns, because everybody was afraid of a cemetery.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came home, and I just passed out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I started-- I came through, and I started to tell them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The next day, I went to school, and nobody said a word.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody-- they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They thought that it was a miracle, that I disappeared.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
